					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You had color subcarrier at 1.79 MHz. That's just <em>wrong</em>, as TVs only understand 3.58 MHz. The counter used to generate the 12 phases seems to be a 21.5 MHz <em>double-pumped</em> counter, which increments at 43 MHz.</div>

